column3: “Ok all I remember from last night is I smoked a half of a bowl. Half. Then proceeded proceeded to eat everything.  Everything?. Yes everything. I woke up fully clothed in bed at 3 am. I am officially afraid of this... until I go to bed. But yeah gets you super relaxed, hungry,  and sleepy as hell. Great strain!!”
“No paranoia and a great muscle relaxer. Good strain for a late night movie or bubble bath.”

“Has everything I want in a indica. Makes me hungry and feeling heavy and slow. I'm eating an apple as I write this and the taste is even better than normal. It's so sweet and crunchy! My body pains feel non existent. I can't even recall my typical complains right now lol. If I wanted I could stay up longer but 3 bong bowls have my bed calling my name soon. Will have a nice ride with this strain. Grows big btw be sure...”
“A nice indica, too much put you in a relax state that can induce good sleep. heavy resin”

“Nice thick buds. Smooth earthy flavor. Not the most crystals I've seen. My batch might be 12-18% THC. I got it for $7 a gram in a medical store. It does make you sleepy and couch lock. It's advertised 80% Indica and 20% Sativa hybrid in the store. Smells earthy. It also creeps up on you.”

“Ended up getting quite a few clones for my indoor In a mixed batch not knowing anything about the strain personally, didn't get my rooms set up in time so I switched to outdoor, and lemme tell ya, massive producers that get huge, and in turn can mold in Oregon climate so watch out.”
“This strain is the perfect one for when your in bed about to go to sleep.”
“I don't know if it's about grower or weed, but made me and friends little paranoid and later sleepy and hungry. Anyway positive feeling was happy, giggly and euphoric.”

“Very strong indica completely couched us, this was a very euphoric and giggly high, that made us question reality and whether or not we were actually awake or if it was a lucid dream. Not recommended if work or societal interactions are in your near future. Smoke it and watch a movie because that's all your brain will manage.”
“this is a couch sitting strain it will slump you”

“this strain will ko you. strong indica that will relax you peacefully. no headache or paranoia. lots of gold resin when cure. dreamy spacey melt to the bed effect after. smooth no cough. again? Absolutely 👍✌👊”

“This will cure your anorexia. ..Just kidding, I'm not a doctor. Or anorexic for that matter. Amazing indica. Full on relaxation except for the slight discomfort brought on by a stomach that just.. can't.. fit.. any.. more. Good night's sleep guaranteed as well. First time giving five stars as the batch was exceptionally good quality as well.”
“My grow was 100% Organic. trying out GO by General Hydroponics. this plant yeild was over 1/2 the grow!”
“PS:Last grow tested @ 22.8% THC. Eases body pain and cramps plus keeps Mind Clear.”
“I am at week 4 of flowering and the plant is 3x denser than my GSC,Big Bud,OG Kush,Green Crack”
“Grows Great smokes even Better!”
“@a4weeks into flowering”
“PS:Last grow tested @ 22.8% THC. Eases body pain and cramps plus keeps Mind Clear.”
“very tasty”
“I am at week 4 of flowering and the plant is 3x denser than my GSC,Big Bud,OG Kush,Green Crack”
“a light smoke with a very hard hitting high”

“1 STRAIN HUNTERS MONEY MAKER in T-5 veg 400W HPS Bloom DWC.1 week to harvest. est. yield 3-4 oz dried and cured.
This is a heavy indica
Smoke it & Relax
Smells like Berry,Kush,Earthy kind of like Bubba Kush 
Next grow ALL MONEY MAKER x 10 will follow up.”
“WOW”
“Sweet aroma.  Very smooth.  Slowly creeps on you, very enjoyable and no sense of paranoia and a good night's sleep.”

“My last grow had 1 Greenhouse Seeds STRAIN Hunters. It yielded 4 times all my other plants. Next Grow I'll be 10 FEM MONEY. I will also be growing 5- OG KUSH, 5-Chemdawg, 6-AK, 2- Lemon haze. I am going to cross all strains. Goal is to increase yield of other straIns.”
“the name speaks for it's self”
“can anyone tell me if this is an auto flowering plant. first time growing”
“Awesome!”
“I am at week 4 of flowering and the plant is 3x denser than my GSC,Big Bud,OG Kush,Green Crack”
“guud shit”
“Great for Pain, Insomnia”

“Gives great clear-headed hight, no paranoia! very nice all arounder.. Could go for a walk with dog or just stay home meditating or watching movie. This gives you a good vibes and relieves stress, making everything beyond normal. 
It hits relatively slow but knocks you out for about 10 min after and last under an hour.”

“Great indica strain! It left me completely relaxed with a clear head yet not completely couch locked. Money Maker is a creeper and within 40 minutes I was seriously contemplating consuming everything in my refrigerator. Just like all reefer it makes me appreciate everything more, so everything I ate tasted amazing! I ripped another bowl after and then hit my bed again appreciating how comfortable the bed actually was...”

“Top Indica. It hits you super hard and will lock you to the couch, super stone with this one. Perfect for at home after work chilling on the couch with a movie and plenty of munch. My eyes got super heavy and my mind slowly faded into a daze. Super relaxing and euphoric. I didn't want to move.

The bud smells real good and grinds up nicely. No feelings of paranoia or anxious thoughts. A new favourite for me. 

couch>”
“very tasty”
“Really nice, very relaxing and tasty”
“Not very strong but a great mellow high.”

“I didn't believe that what I got was this strain. But, after over smoking before work I truly believe this is Money maker! No paranoia and constant zoning out! This strain should be called money loser!”
“Love it!”
“Definitely a favorite to grow! Responds well to a scrog net and lst. Compost tea and soil for best results, definitely. This hurts because I'm a certified organic Hydroponicist.”
“Absolutely fucking amazing strain; great taste, fantastic smell and perfectly sedating effects. My personal favourite strain for insomnia, and for instant stress relief.”
“I am at week 4 of flowering and the plant is 3x denser than my GSC,Big Bud,OG Kush,Green Crack”

“I  picked this strain to help with chronic back pain.  After my first indoor hydro grow it really amazed me with its production.  Really stout colas that will require some support so plan ahead.  This strain has allowed me to cut the amount of pain meds I have to take to 1/3 the dosage I had to use before using cannabis-great results.”

“I decided to try this strain for pain relief.  I started 5 plants in my closet hydro setup and they just thrived.  I ended up making some clones for a friend but she couldn't safely plant them-one is now over 9' tall and has HUGE colas.  Excellent choice for pain and helps me relax.”
“PSS: using new 1000 Watt LED (100-2x5watt)”
“Short effects”
“The effects, medical, negatives are all spot on for me. I really enjoy this strain!”
“Great like a Bubba Kush high yields”
